        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 13 at 7:30PM CDT until June 13 at 8:15PM CDT by NWS Houston/Galveston TX</headline>
        <description>SVRHGX

The National Weather Service in League City has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
South central Montgomery County in southeastern Texas...
North central Harris County in southeastern Texas...

* Until 815 PM CDT.

* At 730 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Tomball,
moving east at 20 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

* Locations impacted include...
Tomball, Greater Greenspoint, Spring, Aldine, The Woodlands,
Willowbrook, Hurricane Harbor Splashtown, Hooks Airport, Hidden
Valley, northern Acres Home, Greater Inwood, and northwestern Bush
Intercontinental Airport.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
